ing to junior staff on how to perform tasks or duties. Travel between branches, as duties may be assigned at any library branchProvide relief as required for any shift in any locationOther duties as may be assigned from time to time Wage Rate:$ 29.77 per hour. Hours of Work: Up to an average of 28 hours per week. Hours and location are subject to change at any time. Base Location: Memorial Branch (Alliston) Please submit your cover letter and resume in one PDF document to jmole@ntpl.ca no later than 4:30PM on Friday, July 21, 2023.Please quote Job Posting # CIRC-072023-02 in the subject line of your email. We thank you for your interest, however; only those selected for an interview will be contacted. The New Tecumseth Public Library is an equal opportunity employer that is committed to inclusive, barrier-free recruitment and selection processes. If contacted for an interview, please advise the recruiter if you require accommodation. Compensation $29.77 Closes: 21 July, 2023 New Tecumseth Public Library Alliston , ON Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
